Gas leakage tragedies and accidents have led to heavy losses over the years. 
So it is very important to detect any gas leakage and prevent any accidents. 
So here we propose a system to detect LPG gas leakage scenarios and provide a security alert to intended users.

You can read the tutorial of this project by using below link.

http://www.embetronicx.com/projects/8051-projects/gas-leakage-detection-system-using-8051/
